;"> </a> <span class="fl">with Five Fabulous Features</span> <a href="javascript:;" onclick="set5dot0Cookie();" class="fl pl10 font-italic hide" style="color:#d14836;"><u>Try it Now!</u></a>  </div>  <div class="announce-screens table" style="margin:20px auto 0; width:1020px;">  <ul>  <li> <div name="newver_ban" class="panel" id="slfirstdiv">  <div class="front">  <div class="pad"><img class="annimgborder" src="${getCdnUrl(\'img\',\'images/slide-screen1.png\')}"></div> </div> <div class="back">  <div class="pad"> <div style="background-color: #4a89dc;z-index: 10000;width: 188px;height: 188px;"> <div class="lh20 font-medium pt20 forumTitle2 tac" style="color: #fff;">Intuitive New UI</div> <div class="qulbl2 tasklistTitle lh23 tac p20" style="color: #fff;">An intuitive new UI that is also faster and makes better use of display space</div> </div> </div> </div>  </li>   <li> <div name="newver_ban" class="panel">  <div class="front">  <div class="pad"><img class="annimgborder" src="${getCdnUrl(\'img\',\'images/slide-screen5.png\')}"></div> </div> <div class="back">  <div class="pad"> <div style="background-color: #4a89dc;z-index: 10000;width: 188px;height: 188px;"> <div class="lh20 font-medium pt20 forumTitle2 tac" style="color: #fff;">Better Resource Utilization</div> <div class="qulbl2 tasklistTitle lh23 tac p20" style="color: #fff; padding:15px;">Get the best out of your team with enhanced resource utilization and work hours</div> </div> </div> </div>  </li>  <li> <div name="newver_ban" class="panel">  <div class="front">  <div class="pad"><img class="annimgborder" src="${getCdnUrl(\'img\',\'images/slide-screen4.png\')}"></div> </div> <div class="back">  <div class="pad"> <div style="background-color: #4a89dc;z-index: 10000;width: 188px;height: 188px;"> <div class="lh20 font-medium pt20 forumTitle2 tac" style="color: #fff;">SLA Automation</div> <div class="qulbl2 tasklistTitle lh23 tac p20" style="color: #fff;">Ensure expectations are met by automating escalations and actions to be performed</div> </div> </div> </div>  </li>  <li> <div name="newver_ban" class="panel">  <div class="front">  <div class="pad"><img class="annimgborder" src="${getCdnUrl(\'img\',\'images/slide-screen2.png\')}"></div> </div> <div class="back">  <div class="pad"> <div style="background-color: #4a89dc;z-index: 10000;width: 188px;height: 188px;"> <div class="lh20 font-medium pt20 forumTitle2 tac" style="color: #fff;">Tighter Integration<br /> with Finance Apps</div> <div class="qulbl2 tasklistTitle lh23 tac p20" style="color: #fff;">Connect with Zoho Invoice or Zoho Books and manage finances with no pain</div> </div> </div> </div>  </li>  <li> <div name="newver_ban" class="panel">  <div class="front">  <div class="pad"><img class="annimgborder" src="${getCdnUrl(\'img\',\'images/slide-screen3.png\')}"></div> </div> <div class="back">  <div class="pad"> <div style="background-color: #4a89dc;z-index: 10000;width: 188px;height: 188px;"> <div class="lh20 font-medium pt20 forumTitle2 tac" style="color: #fff;">Enhanced Chrome Extension</div> <div class="qulbl2 tasklistTitle lh23 tac p20" style="color: #fff;">Whichever tab you are on, taking complete control of projects is just a click away!</div> </div> </div> </div>  </li>  </ul> <div style="display: table; width: 1000px; margin:0px auto; padding-top: 30px;" class="allmilestonestxt2">  <a href="https://www.zoho.com/projects/blog/zoho-projects-5-is-here-and-five-fabulous-reasons-to-love-it.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: underline;" class="fl" onclick="closeNewBanner();">Click here to learn more....</a>  <a href="javascript:;" class="fr" onclick="closeNewBanner();">Okay, got it!</a>  </div>  </div>  </td>  </tr>  </tbody>  </table>  </div>  </div> </div> <script> jQuery(\'[name="newver_ban"]\').hover(function(){  jQuery(this).addClass(\'flip\');  },function(){  jQuery(this).removeClass(\'flip\'); }); setTimeout(function() { jQuery("#slfirstdiv").trigger("mouseover"); setTimeout(function(){ jQuery("