le="width: 0px; height: 0px; position: absolute; border-right: 12px solid transparent ! important; border-left: 12px solid transparent ! important; left: 11px; border-top: 15px solid rgb(252, 109, 100) ! important; top: 26px;"></span> <div class="fl tal inlineBlock" style="background: rgb(240, 240, 240) none repeat scroll 0% 0%; padding: 20px 0px 0px; width: 100%; height:305px">  <ul class="fs15px lh16 text-black" style=" padding: 0px 32px;">  <li>Associate a task with its related bug to easily manage both in the Bug details page.</li>  <li class="pt15">Likewise in the Task details page, associate the relevant bug with the task.</li> <li class="pt15">Also, you can delete the associated tasks or bugs.</li>  </ul> </div>  </div>  <div class="videotab color grn" onclick="jQuery(\'#tab2,#video2\').show();jQuery(\'#tab1,#tab3,#video1,#video3\').hide();" id="bt2">  <span class="tabno">2</span>  <span class="tabtitle">Breakdown complex tasks</span>  </div> <div class="info" id="tab2" name="vtabs" style="display: none;">  <span style="width: 0px; height: 0px; position: absolute; border-right: 12px solid transparent ! important; border-left: 12px solid transparent ! important; left: 11px; border-top: 15px solid rgb(61, 197, 174) ! important; top: 74px;"></span> <div style="height:305px; background: rgb(240, 240, 240) none repeat scroll 0% 0%;" class="fl tal inlineBlock w100per pt20">  <ul class="fs15px lh16 text-black" style="padding: 0px 32px;">  <li>Create subtasks by dragging and dropping the task beneath the main task.</li>  <li class="pt15">Add subtasks from the Task details page.</li> <li class="pt15">Reorder subtasks based on your requirement.</li> <li class="pt15">Convert a subtask into a task.</li>  </ul> </div>  </div>  <div onclick="jQuery(\'#tab3,#video3\').show(); jQuery(\'#tab1,#tab2,#video1,#video2\').hide();" class="videotab color blu" id="bt3">  <span class="tabno">3</span>  <span class="tabtitle">Task dependency in Gantt chart</span>  </div> <div class="inf